videos.description: UNCG wins the opening tip and tosses a quick alley-oop up to open the scoring.
videos.headline: UNCG opens up the scoring with a lob and slam

videos.description: UNCG picks up a steal and Kyrin Galloway goes up for the dunk in transition.
videos.headline: UNCG turning defense into offense

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyus Battle drives through multiple defenders for the layup and the foul.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Tyus Battle drives for the and-1

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyler Lydon catches the alley-oop for the dunk and the foul.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon slams home the lob plus the foul

videos.description: Syracuse's Tyler Lydon hammers down the dunk after Syracuse weaves a couple passes through the UNCG defense.
videos.headline: Tyler Lydon slams down an emphatic dunk

videos.description: UNCG's Diante Baldwin fools the Syracuse defense and goes baseline for the reverse layup.
videos.headline: UNCG's Diante Baldwin goes baseline for the reverse layup

videos.description: UNCG's Diante Baldwin comes up with a steal and goes up for the east two handed dunk.
videos.headline: UNCG's Diante Baldwin picks John Gillon's pocket and takes it for an easy two-handed flush
